    dâoÃđ
    $$
      \1_{B} = \sum_{i=1}^{n}\1_{A_{i}} - \sum_{1 \leq i < j \leq n}\1_{A_{i} \cap A_{j}} + \cdots + (-1)^{n-1}\1_{A_{1} \cap  \cdots \cap  A_{n}}
